COMMERCIAL LICENSE
------------------
TBD is open source under GPL-3.0. If you want to build a commercial product on
it without GPL-3.0's source-disclosure obligations — incorporate it in
closed-source firmware, ship without attribution, negotiate custom OEM terms —
a commercial licence is available.

We also offer:
  - TBD-Core: our core DSP board with all audio, MIDI, and USB I/O assembled;
    connect your own UI board via the 30-pin FFC connector and design your own
    enclosure.
  - Custom Integration: we integrate the ESP32-P4, RP2350, and codec directly
    onto your PCB for full control over form factor, connectors and BOM.
  - Licensed special editions of the TBD-16.

A commercial licence is also the route to use the WebUI in your own product.

Contact dadamachines: https://dadamachines.com/contact/  (see also COMMERCIAL-LICENSE.md)


